videos.description: UConn shows their speed as Christyn Williams gets free for an easy layup.
videos.headline: UConn gets out in transition for easy finish

videos.description: Arike Ogunbowale continues to shine as she freezes the UConn defender and drains the jump shot.
videos.headline: Ogunbowale freezes defender and nails jumper

videos.description: Arike Ogunbowale gets the Irish out and running as she catches the lob and finishes with nice lay in.

videos.description: UConn begins to pull away as Crystal Dangerfield crosses up Notre Dame defender and finishes with a nice scoop lay-in.

videos.description: Freshman Christyn Williams dominates the defending champs as she posts a career-high 28 points, leading the Huskies to an 89-71 win over Notre Dame.

videos.headline: UConn's Williams goes off on the Irish for 28 points

videos.description: Christyn Williams joins Holly Rowe to react to her career-high 28-point outing against Notre Dame and discusses where she gets her competitive fire from.
videos.headline: Williams: I wanted to win this game for my teammates
